text: Veronica Rotin is the eponymous, debut album of Maltese child singer, Veronica Rotin. It was recorded in 2014 by Elton Zarb at FreeTime Studios and contains 14 tracks of covers, mostly songs that Rotin has sung in various singing competitions and on Maltese TV. It was released by Ironic PR & Artist Management, of Marsa, Malta. == Track listing == == References == Category:2014 albums
